DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 05 Community Health Officer Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 25, 2025, 12:34 IST
 District Health Society
 5 Jobs |  Posted On : 25-Aug-2025 |  Gujarat |  Salary : 30,000 to 30,000




FOLLOW

The District Health Society Sabarkantha (DHS Sabarkantha) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 05 Community Health Officer Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application.  Candidates who have completed their B.Sc. can apply for the DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in online mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in Gujarat.

DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 Eligibility Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Community Health Officer	05	B.Sc

DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 21 Years.
The maximum age limit: 40 Years.
Age relaxation is based on the Organisation's norms.

DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process is based on the

Written Test.
Interview.

DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The basic pay: Rs. 30,000/- per month.

How to Apply for the DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025:

Go to the official website.
Visit the DHS Sabarkantha Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligiblity criteria.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Pay the application fee (if needed).
Attach the required documents to the filled application form.
Submit the filled application form before the last date.
Download & take a printout of the filled application form for further use.

Important Dates:

Starting date	21-08-2025
Closing date	30-08-2025
